> createExternalFile

# A before-version-resolution hook installs `releaseIOVersioningFile` pointing at
# a path outside the VCS root. The validate-time check at `inquireVersions.validate`
# saw the original (in-repo) value, so the late-bound override slips past it. The
# `writeVersion` re-check at execute time must reject the external path before the
# file is mutated.
-> releaseIO with-defaults release-version 0.1.0 next-version 0.2.0-SNAPSHOT

